			<div class="content" id="post-content-4010082">
									

<p>Kirby isn't the only one doing Omega-K again!</p>
<p>I hope you all enjoy what is both my first ever GoI format and the first ever Anderson Robotics GoI format!</p>
<p>The design of Finn the Falcon was by me, the structure was designed by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span>, and the CSS was designed by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>!</p>
<p>Also, thanks to <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hot-coles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3997195); return false;">Hot-coles</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/geckoguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3757542); return false;">geckoguy</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;">DrChandra</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;">UraniumEmpire</a></span>, and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span> for crit!</p>
<p>I hope you all enjoy!</p>

							</div>

								
